1.create one Dynamic web project
2.File> new > Dynamic Web Project >next  >next> generate web.xml > Finish
3.Add jersey jars (11 jars)  http:jersey.io/download.html
4.open web.xml and Configure Web.xml   (ctrl+shift+T) to servletcontainer
5.write provider class in  src folder
6.give @Path to provier class
7.every method inside provider in(GET,POST,PUT,DELETE....)
8.Run on Server   /rest/classpath/methodpath....